  "text": "We now establish the uniform bound on\u03c6 \u03b5 . The proof is essentially contained in the work of Song-Tian [CITATION_1] , with the methods generalized to apply to the present situation. Proof. From the previous proposition it suffices to establish a lower bound. We consider the family of Monge-Amp\u00e8re operators for r \u2208 [0, \u221e),",
